(10223, 'tt', 'test', 'tt', '<p>By default, all formats are enabled and allowed in a Quill editor. They can be configured with the <a href=\\\"\\\\&quot;https://quilljs.com/docs/configuration#formats\\\\&quot;\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">formats</a> option. This is separate from adding a control in the <a href=\\\"\\\\&quot;https://quilljs.com/docs/modules/toolbar\\\\&quot;\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">Toolbar</a>. For example, you can configure Quill to allow <strong>bolded</strong> content to be pasted into an editor that has no bold button in the toolbar.</p>', '', NULL, NULL, 'Sue', 'poultrysue@gmail.com', '2025-05-29 18:33:00', 375, '3.00', 'Completed', '2025-05-21 22:33:46', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, '2025-05-22 01:33:46', 1, 'taskfiles/submissions/1749311617_Caterpillar Case Questions and Answers.docx,taskfiles/submissions/1749311619_Historical Speech.docx,taskfiles/submissions/1749312679_WhatsApp Image 2024-06-16 at 22.14.19.jpeg,taskfiles/submissions/1749313041_answer_2_VqFC.docx', 'https://monkbrian.sfo3.cdn.digitaloceanspaces.com/taskfiles/submissions/1749311617_Caterpillar Case Questions and Answers.docx,https://monkbrian.sfo3.cdn.digitaloceanspaces.com/taskfiles/submissions/1749311619_Historical Speech.docx,https://monkbrian.sfo3.cdn.digitaloceanspaces.com/taskfiles/submissions/1749312679_WhatsApp Image 2024-06-16 at 22.14.19.jpeg,https://monkbrian.sfo3.cdn.digitaloceanspaces.com/taskfiles/submissions/1749313041_answer_2_VqFC.docx', '15880,14740,304296,20643', '2025-06-07 19:17:25', '2025-06-21 03:13:08', '2025-07-31 12:25:45', '2025-07-31 09:25:45', 0, NULL, NULL),
